name: Puerto Rico Poster
description:
Title: Puerto Rico
Size: 11" x 14"

This flag is made by the Fresh&Poppy brand due to it's overwhelming desire to explore the world. This poster is perfect for showing country pride or just adding to your collection. 

The flag uses found imagery, textures, and photographs all composed together to create an interesting composition. It also gives a more modern spin on traditional flags.

Frames can be found here:
http://www.ikea.com/us/en/catalog/products/60132521/
or
at many local department stores.

Let me know if you would like a specific flag or if I can help you with anything else!

Enjoy, from Fresh&Poppy : )

name: 2013 Wall Calendar / 2013 Pattern Wall Calendar
description:
Calendars are always things that people need. This simple, yet inviting wall calendar is the perfect size to hang up on a wall in a home, or even to bring to work and show off. 

It has a wire that enables you to hang from anywhere. 

When the month passes, you can easily rip off that month and begin the next with a fresh new patterned month.

Let me know if you'd like more than what I have. 

Enjoy, from Fresh&Poppy!
